<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Griever Guidance</title>
    <style>
      *,
      *::before,
      *::after {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        background: #fff;
        color: #1a1a1a;
      }
      a {
        color: inherit;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section style="max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 80px 24px 64px;">
      <h1
        style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: #111827; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 16px;"
      >
        Griever Guidance
      </h1>
      <p
        style="font-size: 1.125rem; color: #6b7280; margin-bottom: 40px; max-width: 480px;"
      >
        When you lose someone, the last thing you should have to manage is
        logistics. Send funeral and service details to the people who need to
        know, from your phone, in minutes.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://griever-guidance-web.pages.dev/"
        style="display: inline-block; background: #6B7FD4; color: #fff; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500;"
      >
        Download the app
      </a>
    </section>

    <!-- Divider -->
    <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #f3f4f6;" />

    <!-- How it works -->
    <section style="max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 64px 24px;">
      <h2
        style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; color: #111827; margin-bottom: 40px;"
      >
        How it works
      </h2>
      <ol
        style="list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 32px;"
      >
        <li style="display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: flex-start;">
          <span
            style="flex-shrink: 0; width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; background: #eef0fb; color: #6B7FD4; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;"
            >1</span
          >
          <div>
            <strong style="font-size: 15px; color: #111827;"
              >Choose a template</strong
            >
            <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 4px;">
              Select from funeral service details, a passing announcement, or a
              celebration of life.
            </p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li style="display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: flex-start;">
          <span
            style="flex-shrink: 0; width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; background: #eef0fb; color: #6B7FD4; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;"
            >2</span
          >
          <div>
            <strong style="font-size: 15px; color: #111827;"
              >Fill in the details</strong
            >
            <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 4px;">
              Enter the name, date, time, and location. We fill in the rest of
              the message.
            </p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li style="display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: flex-start;">
          <span
            style="flex-shrink: 0; width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; background: #eef0fb; color: #6B7FD4; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600;"
            >3</span
          >
          <div>
            <strong style="font-size: 15px; color: #111827;"
              >Send to your contacts</strong
            >
            <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 4px;">
              Choose who needs to know and send. Everyone receives a clear,
              compassionate text message.
            </p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer
      style="border-top: 1px solid #f3f4f6; padding: 32px 24px; text-align: center;"
    >
      <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #9ca3af;">
        Griever Guidance &mdash; Built with care.
      </p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
